# delegateCallbackQueue

**Instance Property**

The dispatch queue on which delegate callbacks are invoked.

## Declaration

```swift
var delegateCallbackQueue: dispatch_queue_t? { get }
```

## Discussion

Provides the queue set in [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVCaptureTimecodeGenerator/setDelegate(_:queue:)]. If no delegate is assigned, this property is `nil`.

## Handling delegate callbacks

- **delegate**: The delegate that receives timecode updates from the timecode generator.
